                <p class="text-danger">
                    Get powerful features and innovations in your web apps.<br />
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="https://www.scheleder.com">
                        Learn More
                    </a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/images/b2.jpg" alt="Microsoft Azure" class="img-responsive" />
